{"tid":1949204,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呼籲中招警立即自首並向傳媒公開831屠殺真相","createTime":"2020-03-29T13:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T15:18:29.000Z","uid":312125,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"758b4ede7af34869f911771c7dc3c9d773917e06","tid":1949204,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">否則義士厲鬼潛身，唔會放過你，死後落硬地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6cb1d6fc2a9d05be72c77805698ac60575446851","tid":1949204,"uid":265271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"758b4ede7af34869f911771c7dc3c9d773917e06","tid":1949204,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">否則義士厲鬼潛身，唔會放過你，死後落硬地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:10:24.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"6865945b915605e971c1fd6edc09db98e8da181c","tid":1949204,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a6edfd4eb988696611986713de98465367c1edc","tid":1949204,"uid":337760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKZiJge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKZiJge.jpg&h=1ddb5aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【毋忘八三一憤怒 毋忘三三一初衷| 在艱彌厲 戰鬥到底】<br />\n<br />\n下週二，831太子恐襲事件七個月，同時亦是香港首場反修例全民大遊行一週年，其後在6月9號全面爆發反送中抗爭，一年過去抗爭仍然繼續持續，但不容置疑的是街頭抗爭稍有冷卻，但我等相信香港民族的反抗意志絕不會磨滅。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘八三一憤怒，毋忘三三一初衷，悼念逝去的戰友要的不是鮮花蠟燭，完成戰友們的遺願就是最好的悼念方法！<br />\n<br />\n3月31號，懇請香港民族用盡一切辦法，讓泯滅人性者負上應有代價，在艱彌厲戰鬥到底！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港&middot;時代革命<br />\n香港獨立&middot;唯一出路"},{"pid":"ea849d4c92cef8fa9060871ccd9b9857e714ca5d","tid":1949204,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74a1ef0126a10127a83fdc1d7559999ff94925c","tid":1949204,"uid":64138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3119cff06398e206b47338a4f90d67bcde2c8735","tid":1949204,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da27b7df205bea8cfd41c0f2471e65fa6a9215d","tid":1949204,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:26:23.000Z","msg":"食屎狗唔講就冚家產"},{"pid":"1daadd364d0ef2409e15aa22e2d0661c59f5e558","tid":1949204,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"push"}]}